genresAdvancedInfo.name: deep orgcore
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Deep Orgcore is a subgenre of punk rock that emphasizes a DIY ethic and a commitment to underground culture. It is characterized by its fast, aggressive guitar riffs, pounding drums, and shouted vocals. The lyrics often deal with social and political issues, as well as personal struggles and frustrations. Deep Orgcore is beloved by fans for its energy and passion, as well as its rejection of mainstream values and commercialism.
